The SAMA award show will be staged on 31 May and 1 June at Sun City resort in North West province. JOHANNESBURG - Lady Zamar, Black Coffe, DJ Ganyani and Sun-El Musician have been announced as some of the finalists for the Record of the Year Award in the 25th instalment of the South African Music Awards (SAMA). The SAMA award show will be staged on 31 May and 1 June at Sun City resort in North West province.             